author: shazron
msg: Added ability so that unhanded URLs (i.e. custom schemes in a web-page) will notify PhoneGap plugins of this custom url so that the plugins can handle it themselves.
This would give the ability to handle callbacks for OAuth logins (Twitter/Facebook) in the main PhoneGap UIWebview, and not require the ChildBrowser plugin.
